  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 5 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}Oh, well, uh...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 5 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}{f 4 23 0 3 0 25 25}Actually, I'm surprised you remember me.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}I could say the same about you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
