  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 5 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}So, uh... what're you working on?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}A drawing. Why?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 5 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}Uh, no real reason, I guess...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 5 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}{f 4 23 0 3 0 25 25}I just thought it's pretty awesome to have something you're passionate about.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}It's nothing like that. I'm just drawing because I feel like it.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
